WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Okay, we've checked in. What's next?

00:07.000 --> 00:12.000
It's nearly eight o'clock and the plane leaves at 8.30.

00:12.000 --> 00:16.000
How long is the journey? About 10 hours.

00:16.000 --> 00:21.000
10 hours and it's eight hours time difference.

00:21.000 --> 00:26.000
So we'll arrive at 2.30 in the afternoon.

00:26.000 --> 00:28.000
Announcement.

00:29.000 --> 00:31.000
Hello passengers.

00:31.000 --> 00:40.000
Flight CA 938 from London to Beijing was going to leave at 8.30pm.

00:40.000 --> 00:46.000
However, we're sorry to tell you that it will be three hours late.

00:46.000 --> 00:50.000
We'll give you more information as soon as we can.

00:50.000 --> 00:56.000
Three hours late. That means we'll leave at 11.30pm.

00:56.000 --> 01:01.000
So we'll arrive at 5.30 in the afternoon.

01:01.000 --> 01:08.000
Yes, that's right. So we'll need to call your mother and let her know.

